%bcond_without lang
Name:           qqc2-breeze-style
Version:        5.21.5
Release:        0
Summary:        Breeze Style for Qt Quick Controls 2
License:        LGPL-2.1-only OR LGPL-3.0-only
Group:          System/Libraries
URL:            https://www.kde.org
